WEBVTT

00:00:01.602 --> 00:00:06.685
Rođena sam 1993. godine
u sjevernom dijelu Sjeverne Koreje,

00:00:06.709 --> 00:00:09.196
u gradu Hyesanu,

00:00:09.220 --> 00:00:11.931
na granici s Kinom.

00:00:12.949 --> 00:00:15.479
Odrastala sam uz brižne roditelje

00:00:15.503 --> 00:00:17.756
i stariju sestru.

00:00:19.237 --> 00:00:21.678
Prije moje desete godine

00:00:22.516 --> 00:00:25.046
otac je poslan u radni kamp

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:28.281
jer se bavio nezakonitom trgovinom.

00:00:29.042 --> 00:00:31.959
"Nezakonita prodaja" bila je